---
---
<section class="tokenomics" id="tokenomics">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="text-gradient">Dragon-Forged Tokenomics</h2>
      <p>$CHZ blends iconic Charizard energy with disciplined supply mechanics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="glass-card stat-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">💎</div>
        <h4>Total Supply</h4>
        <div class="stat-big">1,000,000,000</div>
        <p>$CHZ</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card stat-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">🔥</div>
        <h4>Burn Mechanism</h4>
        <div class="stat-big">Deflationary</div>
        <p>Auto-Burn Events</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-card stat-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">🛡️</div>
        <h4>Liquidity</h4>
        <div class="stat-big">Battle-Tested</div>
        <p>Locked & Secure</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-grid">
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="dot red"></div>
        <div>
          <h5>Dynamic Burn Events</h5>
          <p>Reduces circulating supply with every major milestone to fuel scarcity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="dot orange"></div>
        <div>
          <h5>Community Vaults</h5>
          <p>Funds cross-chain expansion and real-world utility for the flame-bearers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <div class="dot blue"></div>
        <div>
          <h5>Transparent Governance</h5>
          <p>On-chain voting lets the community decide the next evolution of $CHZ.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tokenomics {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }

  .icon-circle {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: var(--glass);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }

  h4 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-big {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: white;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dot.red { background: #FF1F00; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #FF1F00; }
  .dot.orange { background: #FF4D00; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #FF4D00; }
  .dot.blue { background: #00D4FF; box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00D4FF; }

  h5 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .info-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
